snippet.title: The Beauty Cult's NECTARMANCER - Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Releasing once it's done. Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/739790/The_Beauty_Cults_NECTARMANCER/

Nectarmancer is a gardenvania that combines combat platforming with science-fantasy gardening.  Play as Aisa, the newest Nectarmancer conscripted to serve The Throne, a fascist theocracy bent on exploiting the natural balance and extracting Nectar for their selfish means.

Music by Memnon Sa.
